      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WONDERFUL WORK (2) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but had to settle for a minor placing when a 4 length third over 460m at Geelong, clocking 25.95. Rates highly and will give a great sight. NEO DEVERE (7) boasts a consistent overall record including 13 wins from 52 starts, but missed the frame latest when fifth (34.72) over 595m at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. PAW FABIAN (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at The Meadows behind Unacceptable Nik (30.65) in a Grade 4. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Must be included in calculations. COOL DISGUISE (8) deserves plenty of thought at her first run at this circuit.",
